songs.title: Taxi*
songs.lyrics:
[Verse: Camila Cabello]
Then you catch my eye
Give me a sign
Say you feel right yeah
We ran out of time again, tonight
Happens like this every time
So what you're doing for the rest of your life?

[Pre-Chorus: Camila Cabello]
Baby, keep kissing me softly
Holding me, whispering quietly
Darling, I think that this might be the greatest of story
That's never been, never been, never been, never been easy
It's a new feeling I'm falling

[Chorus: Camila Cabello]
In a New York Taxi Cab
With a-
